name: BACK TO COMMUNITY
description:
Do humans return to the culture of mutual cooperation through digital multidimensionality that looks individualistic?
digital sophisticated tools that seem like saviors become a dilemma in the memory of the culture of gotong royong, the oldest culture. we are brought through forum technology, knowledge sharing and digital community as a new culture of community together. but on the other hand we are met with worry about the digital world about alter ego, anonymous, and others. this will only blur our belief in the digital community, it will definitely be different from the real community culture. trust and distrust will always haunt us but we will continue to hold on to this forever because there is hope there for the culture of gotong royong in today's digital era.

Inspired :
Tarek Pukat
Songket
